{"tid":1692963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 召集各位有投映器既手足 即刻落街直播民間記者會","createTime":"2019-11-04T10:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:28:15.000Z","uid":251119,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78e0830354d9d4e4cb68ed5f1ff3e8e392dfaa67","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"今日黑警曱甴轉左網上播<br />\n佢地冇辦法再扭曲真相<br />\n所以民間記者會絕對拎哂優勢 <br />\n係市民聽到警謊前 <br />\n將呢兩日既警暴同恐怖襲擊公諸於世<br />\n但問題係民記既受眾一直都唔算好大<br />\n今日係一個絕佳機會將民記既力量發揮到最大！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要立即準備8點落區搞投映會！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0875097dcfb7351a4ce415b69dc43bf28ca3228d","tid":1692963,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"哇咁急希望有人睇到<br />\n<br />\n推 順便借位<br />\n<br />\n【認真參考日本社運】想行得遠過藍絲，不如唔好再鬧同路人啲ig？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692734</a>"},{"pid":"607e700eac3eb567c0a93acc35546c76e6725474","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d7618644e3294dc3035da03300b2b98e142af27","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec162b33da1f50d37757ab155660321eb75e9f97","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8730d6dc6a47eb5b639173509810f1b61f19c640","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0615767b2aaedbf87597eb8ea7edaacd0c2c90e3","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c35e9f62905cf7e28af3474d3e55fb2fa08f8cf","tid":1692963,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl